subject: Basketball (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: T. J. Bray, coming off a one-game suspension for disciplinary reasons, scored 20 of his 23 points in the second half as Princeton defeated host Rutgers, 78-73, for its sixth straight win.
